snippet.title: Zuma's Revenge! Game Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out some of the new features & levels for Zuma's Revenge! The sequel to Zuma will be released September 15th at www.PopCap.com.

For more information about the game please visit: www.ZumasRevengeGame.com
